#: ../../F/Formosas-Law.rst:5
msgid "Formosa's Law"
msgstr "Formosa's Law"

#: ../../F/Formosas-Law.rst:7
msgid "n\\."
msgstr "名詞"

#: ../../F/Formosas-Law.rst:9
msgid ""
"\"The truly insane have enough on their plates without us adding to it.\" "
"That is, flaming someone with an obvious mental problem can't make it any "
"better. Most often cited on `alt.usenet.kooks <news:alt.usenet.kooks>`_\\  "
"as a reason *not* to issue a Kook-of the-Month Award; often cited as a "
"companion to :ref:`Godwins-Law`\\."
msgstr ""
"「本物の狂人は、我々が付け加えるまでもなく、すでに十分に手いっぱいなのだ」。つまり、明らかに精神に問題がある人を炎上させても、事態はちっとも良くならない、ということ。最もよく引用されるのは"
" `alt.usenet.kooks <news:alt.usenet.kooks>`_\\ で、Kook-of-the-Month Awardを\\ "
"*出さない*\\ 理由として挙げられる。\\ :ref:`Godwins-Law`\\ の相棒としてもよく引用される。"
